# Build output
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

# Logs
**/logs/
*.log

# Environment / secrets (never bake into image)
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json

# Test projects (not needed in production image)
**/*Tests*/
**/*Test*/

# Git
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# Docs
*.md
docs/

# Docker metadata
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml
railway.toml
